<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Solar Report — {{ system.name }}</title>
<style>
  body {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  h1, h2 {
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .metadata,
  footer {
    color: #6b6b6b;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Solar Report — {{ system.name }}</h1>
<p class="metadata">
  Period: {{ summary.start_date.isoformat() }} to {{ summary.end_date.isoformat() }}<br>
  Generated: {{ generated_at.isoformat(timespec="seconds") }}<br>
  System: {% if system.location %}{{ system.location }} · {% endif %}{{ system.installed_kwp }} kWp
</p>
<hr>
<main>
{{ body_markdown | markdown }}
</main>
<hr>
<footer>
  Report generated by solar-report. Numbers are computed from source data; interpretive text is model-generated.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
